{"tid":732993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[林鄭擺香港上台] 林鄭：多邊貿易體制昨日被「某國」破壞了","createTime":"2018-07-07T11:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T12:36:46.000Z","uid":149494,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"c2b909755e863f93c7f946150441dcbcdf0b9f9b","tid":732993,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰昨日開打，特首林鄭月娥今早在一個論壇上致辭時表示，多邊貿易體制以及經濟全球化的法律秩序，就在昨日被「某個國家」破壞了。特區政府會保持警惕，評估中美貿易戰由制裁以至增加關稅所帶來的影響。後來她又表示，「回想」起中國國家主席習近平曾在一個國際論壇上發言，稱「你可以把門關上，將風雨阻隔；但關上門，同時會令屋內的人不能接觸空氣與陽光」，她認為當中的寓言值得大家深思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭無端白事引戰，明擺香港上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc5b1e39d8ab5856f7c6b8e652c4351e1b4f75a","tid":732993,"uid":58247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"乜刁大大個竇唔閂門架?"},{"pid":"b0fbaae036f6ce707cdd1e2fe90a80ae530fb387","tid":732993,"uid":38391,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"中國對外關係越差香港就越多錢揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個On9林鄭為咗刷鞋連自己本錢都攞出嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde85d61a59af8f69fd68956ab5e272560cb33f9","tid":732993,"uid":70336,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"得罪埋老美到時真係要背靠終國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e80b46016771a917f1afc5eb6d2567bee66f1fb","tid":732993,"uid":4783,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"刷錯鞋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能雜種就係想香港繼續做白手套買野<br />\n點知條傻仔跳出黎譴責美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no